The {$\nu_e$}{} and {$\overline{\nu}_e$}{} appearance data are shown in Fig. \ref{fig:nueSpec}, binned as a function of reconstructed energy and $\alpha_{LEM}$. The bins between 5 and 8$\,$GeV are shown for display purposes, but are combined into a single bin in the fitting procedure.
